            <article class="a-main  " data-article-url="https://www.wired.co.uk/article/gender-neutral-toilets-design" data-article-type="article" data-article-uid="7Ol4xGKrVwq" data-meta-title="The curse of the phantom pooer shows why gender neutral toilet designs aren’t working | WIRED UK">
