                                    <h1 class="a-header__title">The curse of the phantom pooer shows why gender neutral toilet designs aren’t working</h1>

                                    <div class="a-header__teaser has-bbcode"><p class="bb-p">It's not enough to change a sign or take away urinals – it’s time for companies to rethink their entire bathroom provision</p></div>

                                <hr class="a-header__separator" />

                                <div class="a-header__about">

                                        <div class="a-header__byline">

                                        <span class="a-header__byline-item">
                                            <span class="a-header__byline-prefix">By</span>
                                            <span class="a-header__byline-name"><a href="/profile/natasha-bernal">Natasha Bernal</a></span>
                                        </span>


                                        </div>

                                            <div class="a-header__date">02 Mar 2020</div>
                                </div>


