                                <li class="c-card-section__card-listitem js-c-card-section__card-listitem ">
                                    <article class="c-card c-card--switcher">
                                    		<a href="/article/facebook-google-diversity-growth" class="c-card__link c-card__link--article ">There&#x27;s a lot Facebook and Google can learn from Betamax and VHS</a>

                                    	<div class="c-card__obj">
                                    		<div class="c-card__obj__header">
                                    			<div class="c-card__images">

                                    						<div class="c-card__image c-card__image--custom ">
                                    								        <picture>
